        Creates a new Fragment header.
        Parameters:
        id - 32-bit fragment identification value
        fragment_offset - 13-bit offset, in 8-octet units, of the data relative to the start of the Fragmentable Part of the original packet
        more_fragments - MF flag: true = more fragments, false = last fragment
